title: Herb Alpert on Chet Baker
description: Herb Alpert's thoughts on legendary jazz trumpet player Chet Baker, excerpted from the NYU Steinhardt Jazz Interview Series on November 14, 2015 hosted by Dave Schroeder.  Full interview can be viewed at: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oYvf_r0n4fk
